---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Note from "../../components/Note.astro";
const title = "switches — ecute.club";
---
<BaseLayout {title}>
  <article class="container">
    <h1>switches</h1>
    <p>mechanical ways to connect or select circuits. two axes: <em>poles</em> (how many circuits) and <em>throws</em> (positions).</p>

    <table class="cute">
      <thead><tr><th>type</th><th>expands to</th><th>use</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>spst</td><td>single-pole single-throw</td><td>on/off</td></tr>
        <tr><td>spdt</td><td>single-pole double-throw</td><td>choose a or b</td></tr>
        <tr><td>dpdt</td><td>double-pole double-throw</td><td>flip two lines at once (e.g., polarity reverse)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>mom.</td><td>momentary</td><td>returns when released</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>spdt contact map</h2>
    <div class="diagram halo-strong" role="img" aria-label="spdt common to NO/NC">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 680 220" width="100%" height="auto">
        <rect x="0" y="0" width="680" height="220" rx="16" fill="var(--card)"/>
        <circle cx="120" cy="120" r="8" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="540" cy="80" r="8" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="540" cy="160" r="8" fill="currentColor"/>
        <line x1="128" y1="118" x2="540" y2="80" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4"/>
        <line x1="128" y1="122" x2="540" y2="160" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4" opacity=".35"/>
        <text x="96" y="150" class="mono">COM</text>
        <text x="560" y="86" class="mono">NO</text>
        <text x="560" y="166" class="mono">NC</text>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <Note variant="try">wire an LED to NO and another to NC (with resistors). move the lever and watch which one lights.</Note>
    <Note variant="fact">momentary = returns when released. toggle = stays where you leave it.</Note>

    <h2>debounce</h2>
    <p>mechanical contacts bounce for a few ms. in code, debounce 10–50 ms or hardware RC + schmitt trigger.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
